Daily Check {
	Find appointments.csv
	Find orders.csv
	Build local database of appointments
	For each order {
		If order does not exist locally, create it
		If the order exists and is closed, skip to the next order
		If the order already has an appointment, check its validity
		If it is valid, skip the next 5 steps
			Look for valid appointment with same patient id and acceptable appointment type for order
			If found, associate appointment with order
			Check date range for approval
			Check date range for out-of-pocket
			Check date range for pre-procedure 
		If the order has an appointment and the date has passed close the order
		
	}
}

We are keeping track of whether all procedure orders:
- Have insurance approval
- Have been contacted about out-of-pocket
- Have been given pre-procedure instructions
- Have an appointment